001package edu.cnm.deepdive.leavemealone.model.entity;
002
003
004import androidx.annotation.NonNull;
005import androidx.room.ColumnInfo;
006import androidx.room.Embedded;
007import androidx.room.Entity;
008import androidx.room.Index;
009import androidx.room.PrimaryKey;
010import edu.cnm.deepdive.leavemealone.model.pojo.GPSCoord;
011import java.time.Instant;
012
013@Entity(
014    tableName = "location",
015    indices = {})
016public class Location {
017
018    @PrimaryKey(autoGenerate = true)
019    @ColumnInfo(name = "location_id")
020    private long id;
021
022    @ColumnInfo(name = "secure", index = true)
023    private boolean secure;
024
025    @ColumnInfo(name = "tracked", index = true)
026    private boolean tracked;
027
028    @Embedded
029    private GPSCoord gpsCoord;
030
031    @ColumnInfo(name = "timestamp", index = true)
032    @NonNull
033    private Instant timestamp = Instant.now();
034
035    public long getId() {
036        return id;
037    }
038
039    public void setId(long id) {
040        this.id = id;
041    }
042
043    public boolean isSecure() {
044        return secure;
045    }
046
047    public void setSecure(boolean secure) {
048        this.secure = secure;
049    }
050
051    public boolean isTracked() {
052        return tracked;
053    }
054
055    public void setTracked(boolean tracked) {
056        this.tracked = tracked;
057    }
058
059    public GPSCoord getGpsCoord() {
060        return gpsCoord;
061    }
062
063    public void setGpsCoord(GPSCoord gpsCoord) {
064        this.gpsCoord = gpsCoord;
065    }
066
067    @NonNull
068    public Instant getTimestamp() {
069        return timestamp;
070    }
071
072    public void setTimestamp(@NonNull Instant timestamp) {
073        this.timestamp = timestamp;
074    }
075}
